result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 案内には朝6時開店とあるが、朝6時10分に行ったらまだ開店準備中。完全に営業開始になるのは30分くらいかな〰。香港のマクドナルドはどこも結構混んでるのゆったりできないがここはちょっと穴場。近くの九龍公園からは直接つながってるので公園の散策での一休みにも、公園内の店舗よりこちらがお勧め。
頗整潔且尚算寬敞，找位子不太難。
下午茶餐超抵食$16有麭有飲品
Tempat bersih pelayanan okay, awas hati2 ada beberapa makanan non halal food disini
是每一個香港人都會到過的地方。

result.adr_address: 33 Canton Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 33 Canton Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: China Hong Kong City

reviews.text:
This place is an absolute eye opener. It was below our hotel and linked with our rail station. Yes, where in the UK would you get a huge complex like this dedicated to a huge travel hub, its crazy.
The prices where excellent, something for everyone, huge amount of passenger footfall but the size of the place is just huge.
Every train, every taxi and every bus was absolutely on time.
Very easy to navigate around the city as there are lots of street signs as well as a very efficient public transport system. Food is really great, too!
You can find ferry’s to Macau, Nanshan, Lian hua San, and many more places to mainland china. There are many brands outlets store are there. Good place to shop.

reviews.author_name: Martin C. Drot de Gourville Chazarène
reviews.text: It is most enchanting city of the world... always sleepness
This place goes on forever.  Wear your walking shoes and just enjoy yourself.
